# R3F World Movement Rule

- Keep topDown movement based on world-group translation (`worldRef`) instead of moving camera position directly.
- Keep collision checks in `useWorldMovement` (`isOnFloor`, wall/bookshelf/pillar rect intersection) as the single movement gate.
- Reuse shared constants from `src/data/floorPlan.ts` (`PLAYER_RADIUS_M`, `WALL_THICKNESS_M`, `FLOOR_HEIGHT_M`).
- When changing controls, preserve compatibility between camera mode switching and world translation.
